15:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda kasallik varag'i 2026-yil 1-iyuldan boshlab sug'urta stajiga (DSSF ga badallar to'lash stajiga) asoslangan yangi tizim bo'yicha to'lanadi. Ish beruvchi kalendar yilda mehnatga layoqatsizlikning birinchi 5 kalendar kunini o'z mablag'laridan to'laydi, 6-kundan boshlab to'lovni bevosita Davlat sug'urta ijtimoiy fondi (DSSF) amalga oshiradi. Kasallik to'lovini olish huquqiga ega bo'lish uchun kamida 6 oylik sug'urta staji talab qilinadi. To'lov miqdori sug'urta stajiga qarab belgilanadi: 5 yilgacha stajda — o'rtacha ish haqining 60%, 5 dan 8 yilgacha — 80%, 8 yildan ortiq — 100%. Kasallik varag'i biriktirilgan poliklinikada rasmiylashtiriladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash uchun o'rtacha kunlik ish haqi oxirgi 12 oydagi hisoblangan ish haqi summasini shu davrdagi ish kunlari soniga bo'lish orqali aniqlanadi. Agar xodim 12 oydan kam ishlagan bo'lsa, haqiqiy ish davri olinadi. Kasallik to'lovining minimal miqdori minimal ish haqidan (1 271 000 so'm/oy) hisoblashdan past bo'lishi mumkin emas. Eslatma: 2026-yil 1-yanvardan homiladorlik va tug'ish nafaqalari bevosita DSSF mablag'laridan to'lanmoqda, vaqtinchalik mehnatga layoqatsizlik nafaqalari (kasallik varag'i) esa 2026-yil 1-iyuldan DSSFning to'g'ridan-to'g'ri to'lovlariga o'tmoqda."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"To'lanadigan kasallik varag'ining maksimal muddati — yiliga 182 kalendar kungacha. Sil kasalligi bo'lsa — 240 kungacha. Bu muddat tugagandan keyin TIEK qaror qabul qiladi: kasallikni uzaytirish yoki nogironlikni belgilash. 14 yoshgacha kasal bolaga qarov uchun 14 kalendar kungacha, nogiron bolaga — 30 kungacha to'lanadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Kasallik varag'i bo'yicha to'lovlar "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/jshshs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"JShShS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" 12% va "}],["$","$La","3",{"href":"/uz/calculator/ish-haqi","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"IJPH"}],["$","$1","4",{"children":" 0,1% ga tortiladi, lekin ijtimoiy soliqqa tortilmaydi. Kasallik varag'i to'lanmaydi: sog'liqqa qasddan zarar yetkazish natijasida yuzaga kelgan bo'lsa, hibsda bo'lgan davrda, ish haqi saqlanmagan ta'til davrida. Ish beruvchi kasallik varag'ini qabul qilishi va 10 ish kuni ichida hisob-kitob qilishi shart."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],"$L1a"]}]]}],"$L1b","$L1c","$L1d"]}]
